   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica LV</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Quae fuerant, vivente anima olim, mortua membra</l>
     <l n="2">absque anima tandem claudit humata lapis.</l>
     <l n="3">Corporis affecti aerumnas novus incola coeli</l>
     <l n="4">spiritus hic gaudet deposuisse graves.</l>
     <l n="5">Quare animam Iani seu corpus flere, viator,</l>
     <l n="6">frustra hoc, sero illud, vanus uterque dolor.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
